    "updated_at": "2014-01-28T18:15:46Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think we should put it in the upper right - because we already send other notification to that general vicinity, and it feels more natural to have one place (notification area is there, and this is just a persistent indicator notifying the user of the mode she's in).\n\nIf we want this indicator to be visible at all times, the file menu bar, but aligned to the notification area, is a natural choice. Otherwise, the edge of the notification area itself also works.\n"
  },
